Dialogue: 100,0:00:36.46,0:00:38.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯, 你还好吗? \N{\rENG}Lars, are you okay?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:38.57,0:00:40.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}幸亏有你的泡泡...\N{\rENG}Thanks to your bubble...
Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.97,0:00:43.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我的骨头只断了一点点\N{\rENG}my bones are only a little broken.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:43.64,0:00:47.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我的也是\N{\rENG}My bones, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:48.18,0:00:50.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}伙计, 那些女巨人对你生了那么大气\N{\rENG}Dude, those giant ladies were furious with you.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:50.68,0:00:52.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们是钻石\N{\rENG}They're the diamonds.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:52.05,0:00:54.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们已经盯上我妈6000年了, \N{\rENG}They've been after my mom for 6,000 years,
Dialogue: 100,0:00:54.72,0:00:56.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而现在她们又盯上了我\N{\rENG}and now they're after me.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:56.38,0:00:58.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}快点, 我们得走了\N{\rENG}Come on. We got to move.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.36,0:01:06.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们该怎么离开这个星球? \N{\rENG}How are we supposed to get off this planet?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:06.99,0:01:09.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你真的知道你在往哪走吗? \N{\rENG}Do you even know where you're going?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:09.16,0:01:12.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不, 我也是第一次来这里\N{\rENG}No. This is my first time here, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:12.17,0:01:14.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这真是糟透了\N{\rENG}This is so messed up.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:14.57,0:01:15.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们能吃什么? \N{\rENG}What are we gonna eat?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:16.00,0:01:19.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果你喜欢吃石头的话 石头有的是\N{\rENG}There's tons of food if you like rocks for dinner.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:19.44,0:01:20.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}盐也算一种石头, 对吧? \N{\rENG}Salt is a rock, right?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:20.88,0:01:24.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}或许往土上撒点盐也能当饭吃\N{\rENG}Maybe we can season some dirt and make a meal.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等下! \N{\rENG}Wait!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:28.35,0:01:29.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...\N{\rENG}Uh...
Dialogue: 100,0:01:29.58,0:01:31.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}抱歉\N{\rENG}Sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:32.19,0:01:33.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他们发现我们了! \N{\rENG}They found us!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:34.92,0:01:36.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}-快跑! -等等! \N{\rENG}-Run! -Wait!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:36.26,0:01:38.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果我们静止不动的话, 它就看不到我们! \N{\rENG}If we stand perfectly still, it won't see us!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:39.03,0:01:41.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我在电影里看到过\N{\rENG}I saw it in a movie once.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:45.63,0:01:47.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}听起来不错\N{\rENG}That sounds good.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:47.10,0:01:51.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...我们得躲开了! \N{\rENG}Uh... We should probably move!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:51.71,0:01:53.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊! \N{\rENG}Aah!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:53.71,0:01:57.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我想那部电影是关于恐龙的\N{\rENG}I think that movie was about dinosaurs.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:58.88,0:02:00.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯, 快! \N{\rENG}Lars, come on!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:00.21,0:02:02.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔! \N{\rENG}Whoa!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:08.06,0:02:10.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们该怎么做? 会发生什么? \N{\rENG}What are we gonna do? What's gonna happen?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:10.73,0:02:13.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们得逃跑 我们会没事的! \N{\rENG}We're gonna run, and we're gonna be okay!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:13.33,0:02:14.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不! \N{\rENG}No!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:14.23,0:02:16.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你没理解我的意思! \N{\rENG}You just don't get it!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:16.93,0:02:19.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我讨厌一味躲避! \N{\rENG}I hate being scared all the time!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.67,0:02:22.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我害怕所有事, 除了烘焙\N{\rENG}I was scared of everything except baking.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:22.84,0:02:25.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}实际上, 我也害怕那个\N{\rENG}Actually, I was scared of that, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.74,0:02:29.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我甚至都不敢尝试做果仁蜜饼, 因为看起来太难了! \N{\rENG}I never even tried making baklava 'cause it looked so hard!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.91,0:02:33.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我从没有胆量保护任何人...\N{\rENG}I never had the guts to stick up for anybody...
Dialogue: 100,0:02:33.11,0:02:34.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}甚至我自己! \N{\rENG}not even me!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:34.82,0:02:39.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而现在我像个怂逼大屌丝似的躲在一个太空建筑下面! \N{\rENG}And now I'm hiding again like a big cowardly loser under some space building!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.75,0:02:42.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不要这样打击自己, 拉尔斯\N{\rENG}Don't beat yourself up like that, Lars.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:42.09,0:02:44.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}打击是那些杀人机器的工作\N{\rENG}That's what the killer robots are for.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:44.59,0:02:46.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}-快! -下面! \N{\rENG}-Quickly! -Down here!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:47.26,0:02:50.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文! 万一这是个陷阱呢? \N{\rENG}Steven! What if it's a trap?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:50.77,0:02:53.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...我不认为我们有的选! \N{\rENG}Uh... I don't think we have a choice!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:53.97,0:02:55.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊! \N{\rENG}Aah!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:01.54,0:03:03.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真险啊, 对吧? \N{\rENG}Close one, huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.38,0:03:04.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错, 但谁--\N{\rENG}Yeah, but who --
Dialogue: 100,0:03:04.31,0:03:06.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}别担心\N{\rENG}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:08.38,0:03:09.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们现在安全了\N{\rENG}You're safe now.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:09.52,0:03:11.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们不会伤害你\N{\rENG}We're not gonna hurt you.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:11.05,0:03:15.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谢谢, 不论你们是...\N{\rENG}Thank you, whoever you...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:18.69,0:03:19.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没事, 拉尔斯\N{\rENG}It's okay, Lars.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:19.86,0:03:21.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谢谢你救了我们\N{\rENG}Thank you for saving us.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:21.63,0:03:24.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真是怪了 他们是什么? \N{\rENG}How bizarre. What are they?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.23,0:03:27.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但可以肯定他们和我们见过的宝石人不一样\N{\rENG}They certainly don't look like gems we've ever seen before.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:30.50,0:03:31.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}快, 这里! \N{\rENG}Come, this way!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:31.84,0:03:33.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这里, 快! \N{\rENG}This way, come!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:33.88,0:03:36.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文, 等等-这真是个好主意吗? \N{\rENG}Steven, wait. - Is this really a good idea?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:36.71,0:03:40.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们看起来...不一样, 我觉得我们可以信任她们\N{\rENG}They seem...different. I think we can trust them.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:45.32,0:03:50.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃, 不好意思, 但, 呃, 你要带我们去哪里? \N{\rENG}Uh, excuse me, but, um, where are you taking us?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:50.19,0:03:52.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}某个早已被遗忘的地方\N{\rENG}Somewhere long forgotten.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}属于无处可归者的归所\N{\rENG}Where only those who don't belong belong.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:55.50,0:03:58.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}听起来像是我这种人的去处\N{\rENG}- Sounds like my kind of place.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.37,0:03:59.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这里不会碰巧\N{\rENG}You don't happen to have
Dialogue: 100,0:03:59.77,0:04:02.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有卖快餐的小店吧? \N{\rENG}any fast-food joints around there, do you?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:02.50,0:04:06.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔! \N{\rENG}Whoa!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:06.44,0:04:08.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是什么地方? \N{\rENG}What is this place?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:08.28,0:04:11.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}宝宝基地\N{\rENG}A kindergarten.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.45,0:04:14.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}超超超大的那种\N{\rENG}A really, really big one.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:20.25,0:04:21.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们回来了! \N{\rENG}We're back!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:21.29,0:04:22.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们来了! \N{\rENG}Here we are!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:22.19,0:04:23.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}可以出来了! \N{\rENG}It's okay to come out!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:23.59,0:04:26.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦, 感谢老天, 我希望你们没被跟踪\N{\rENG}Oh, thank goodness. I hope you weren't followed.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.36,0:04:28.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们没被跟踪吧? 你确定吗? \N{\rENG}You weren't, right? You double-checked?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:28.86,0:04:32.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们被跟踪了! \N{\rENG}You've been followed!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:32.87,0:04:34.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃, 嗨! \N{\rENG}Uh, hi!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:34.24,0:04:37.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃, 别担心-我没有危险的\N{\rENG}Uh, don't worry. - I'm not a threat or anything.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没事的, 蔷薇辉石\N{\rENG}It's okay, Rhodonite.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:39.97,0:04:42.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}放松, 我们带他们来这里的\N{\rENG}Relax. We brought them here.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.04,0:04:43.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他们和我们是一伙的\N{\rENG}They're with us.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:43.14,0:04:44.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们能信任他们吗? \N{\rENG}Can we trust them?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.58,0:04:46.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}-当然-我觉得可以\N{\rENG}-Sure. -I think so.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.05,0:04:47.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}-大家好! -呃? \N{\rENG}-Everyone! -Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:47.38,0:04:50.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一个奇异的幻像出现在了我眼前\N{\rENG}A wondrous vision has appeared before me.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:50.25,0:04:54.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}金红石双胞胎会带回一个--不, 两个--\N{\rENG}The twins of rutile will bring one -- no, two --
Dialogue: 100,0:04:54.76,0:04:56.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}陌生人到我们目前的躲藏处\N{\rENG}strangers to our current place of hiding.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:56.99,0:04:58.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们知道的, 帕德玛蓝宝石\N{\rENG}We know, Padparadscha.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你的预言已经发生了\N{\rENG}Your prediction already happened.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:00.13,0:05:02.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他们在地表被那些\N{\rENG}They were being chased up on the surface
Dialogue: 100,0:05:02.33,0:05:04.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}恐怖的机器追赶着\N{\rENG}by one of those terrible robonoids.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:04.40,0:05:07.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}别告诉我你们试图与那种东西战斗\N{\rENG}Don't tell me you tried to fight those things.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:07.23,0:05:08.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不, 不, 当然不\N{\rENG}No, no. Of course not.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:08.90,0:05:11.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们把他俩拉到地下之前\N{\rENG}These two were about to be scanned
Dialogue: 100,0:05:11.07,0:05:12.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他俩险些就被扫描到了\N{\rENG}when we pulled them under.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.74,0:05:13.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}时机刚刚好\N{\rENG}We were just in time.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:13.98,0:05:16.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让我看看\N{\rENG}Let me see.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:18.81,0:05:21.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...\N{\rENG}Uh...
Dialogue: 100,0:05:21.12,0:05:22.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊! \N{\rENG}Aah!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:22.82,0:05:28.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他们看起来不像是宝石人\N{\rENG}They don't look like gems.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:28.26,0:05:29.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我就是这么说的! \N{\rENG}That's what I said!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:29.69,0:05:31.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我也是这么说的! \N{\rENG}I said the same thing!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.09,0:05:33.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗨! 我是史蒂文, 我是个宝石人\N{\rENG}Hi! I'm Steven. I'm a gem.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:33.76,0:05:35.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃, 半个宝石人\N{\rENG}Well, half-gem.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.10,0:05:38.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是拉尔斯, 他是个人类\N{\rENG}And this is Lars. He's all human.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:38.17,0:05:44.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}难怪你们看起来如此不同寻常\N{\rENG}That's why you look so unusual.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:44.71,0:05:46.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}"我们"看起来不同寻常?! \N{\rENG}We look unusual?!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.51,0:05:47.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然! \N{\rENG}Of course you do!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:47.78,0:05:50.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你不能就这么在地表乱逛! \N{\rENG}You can't just walk around on the surface like that!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:50.31,0:05:52.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是个残品--就像我们其余所有人! \N{\rENG}You're off-color -- just like the rest of us!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.01,0:05:55.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}残品是什么意思? \N{\rENG}What do you mean, off-color?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.88,0:05:57.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你懂的, 错误的\N{\rENG}You know, wrong.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:57.62,0:05:58.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不正确的\N{\rENG}Not, right.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.79,0:06:00.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}有瑕疵的\N{\rENG}Flawed.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:00.15,0:06:04.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等, 我没看出你们有任何问题啊\N{\rENG}Wait, I don't see anything wrong with you guys.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:04.09,0:06:08.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}像我们这样的宝石人是无用的\N{\rENG}Gems like us aren't needed.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:08.83,0:06:15.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}帕德玛只能预言刚刚发生过的事情\N{\rENG}Padparadscha can only predict things that just happened.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:15.64,0:06:17.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}萤石来了! \N{\rENG}Here comes Fluorite!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:18.01,0:06:21.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而像我这样的融合体是不可原谅的\N{\rENG}And a fusion like me is unforgivable.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:21.31,0:06:24.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当我的--我们的摩根石发现之后, \N{\rENG}When my -- our Morganite found out,
Dialogue: 100,0:06:24.48,0:06:26.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这么说吧-我们被替换了\N{\rENG}let's just say we were replaced.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:26.98,0:06:28.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我们的故事可不算什么! \N{\rENG}But my story's nothing!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:28.38,0:06:31.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是指, 萤石, 你现在是多少个宝石人了? \N{\rENG}I mean, Fluorite, - how many gems are you now?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:31.65,0:06:32.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}六个\N{\rENG}Six.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:32.65,0:06:37.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也许会更多, 如果我们遇到合适的宝石人的话\N{\rENG}Maybe more, if we meet the right gem.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:37.69,0:06:39.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还有我们! \N{\rENG}And then there's us!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:39.16,0:06:41.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是说, 你不是个融合体? \N{\rENG}You mean, you're not a fusion?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:41.53,0:06:44.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们只是一个出错的金红石\N{\rENG}We're just a rutile that came out wrong.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:44.67,0:06:47.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们幸存了下来-因为其他所有的金红石\N{\rENG}We survived - because all the other rutiles
Dialogue: 100,0:06:47.84,0:06:49.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在我们出生时都被吓跑了\N{\rENG}ran away when we emerged.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.60,0:06:52.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们幸存了下来, 因为她们害怕我们\N{\rENG}We survived because they were afraid of us.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:52.87,0:06:54.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}害怕你们? \N{\rENG}Afraid of you?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:54.24,0:06:57.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以你们一生都在躲避\N{\rENG}So you've been hiding your whole lives.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:57.95,0:07:00.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果它们发现了你们会怎么样? \N{\rENG}What happens if they find you?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:00.68,0:07:03.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们会被...\N{\rENG}We'll be...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:03.52,0:07:04.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}粉碎\N{\rENG}Shattered.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.52,0:07:08.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}-哦 -不! \N{\rENG}-Oh. -No!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:08.96,0:07:10.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦\N{\rENG}Oh.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:12.73,0:07:16.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊! 你们就是被跟踪了! 他们要发现我们了! \N{\rENG}Ah! You were followed! They're gonna find us!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:16.03,0:07:17.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他们会将我们分开的! \N{\rENG}They're gonna break us!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:17.70,0:07:18.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是我们的错! \N{\rENG}This is our fault!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.93,0:07:20.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果不是因为我们, 你们也不会出事的! \N{\rENG}If it wasn't for us, you'd be fine!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:20.87,0:07:22.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们不能抛弃你们不管啊\N{\rENG}We couldn't just leave you there.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.70,0:07:23.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们得做点什么\N{\rENG}We had to do something.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:23.87,0:07:27.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文? 我们该怎么办? \N{\rENG}Steven? What're we gonna do?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.04,0:07:28.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所有人躲起来! \N{\rENG}Everyone hide!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.05,0:07:34.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}小心, 所有人! 我们要被发现了! \N{\rENG}Careful, everyone! We're about to be found!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.66,0:07:49.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯...\N{\rENG}Lars...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.23,0:07:51.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}害怕是没关系的\N{\rENG}It's okay to be afraid.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.67,0:07:56.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.65,0:08:05.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦, 不! \N{\rENG}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:05.41,0:08:07.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们得做点什么! \N{\rENG}We got to do something!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.58,0:08:08.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯! \N{\rENG}Lars!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:18.59,0:08:20.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯\N{\rENG}Lars!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:20.29,0:08:23.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}害怕是没关系的\N{\rENG}It's okay to be afraid.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:27.77,0:08:30.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦, 我的天! 拉尔斯! \N{\rENG}Oh, my gosh! Lars!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.37,0:08:32.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}它们是要扫描你的宝石! \N{\rENG}They were trying to scan your gem!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:32.17,0:08:33.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}它们根本看不见你! \N{\rENG}They can't see you at all!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:33.71,0:08:34.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧! \N{\rENG}All right!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:34.78,0:08:36.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看来要翻盘了! \N{\rENG}Looks like the tables have turned!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:36.44,0:08:37.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}-人类拉尔斯\N{\rENG}-Human Lars.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:37.95,0:08:41.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一个最非凡的幻像-占据了我的脑海! \N{\rENG}I've been possessed - by the most marvelous vision!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:42.02,0:08:43.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊? \N{\rENG}Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:43.12,0:08:47.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你, 人类拉尔斯, 没有宝石\N{\rENG}You, human Lars, are gemless,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:47.15,0:08:49.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}因而不会被那些机器伤害到\N{\rENG}and will be safe from the robonoids,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:49.69,0:08:52.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}因为它们只瞄准宝石! \N{\rENG}which only target gems!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:59.47,0:09:02.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是我这辈子做过的最酷的事了\N{\rENG}I think that's the coolest thing I've ever done in my life.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:02.67,0:09:04.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还没结束呢\N{\rENG}It's not over yet.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:20.42,0:09:21.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哈? \N{\rENG}Huh?
Dialogue: 100,0:09:26.43,0:09:29.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦-护盾有反射功能\N{\rENG}Oh. - The shield is reflective.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:29.43,0:09:32.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}帕德玛, 快回来! 躲起来! \N{\rENG}Padparadscha, come back! Hide!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:37.61,0:09:39.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.17,0:09:40.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧\N{\rENG}Okay.
Dialogue: 100,0:09:40.94,0:09:42.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧! \N{\rENG}Okay!
Dialogue: 100,0:09:52.72,0:09:55.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}尝尝这个! \N{\rENG}Eat this!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.03,0:10:05.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯! \N{\rENG}Lars!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:05.20,0:10:08.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯? \N{\rENG}Lars?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:08.20,0:10:09.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯? \N{\rENG}Lars?
Dialogue: 100,0:10:09.47,0:10:10.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我以为我们做不到的! \N{\rENG}I didn't think we were gonna make it!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:10.87,0:10:12.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}-那真是太妙了! -拉尔斯, 你太棒了\N{\rENG}-That was amazing! -Lars, that was so great.
Dialogue: 100,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}-你太伟大了-我们快赢了! \N{\rENG}-You were amazing. -We're winning!
Dialogue: 100,0:10:14.21,0:10:16.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们要赢了! \N{\rENG}We're winning!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.13,0:11:06.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔\N{\rENG}Whoa.
Dialogue: 100,0:11:06.43,0:11:08.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}发生了什么? \N{\rENG}What happened?
Dialogue: 100,0:11:09.03,0:11:10.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦, 我的天! \N{\rENG}Oh, my!
Dialogue: 100,0:11:10.36,0:11:12.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}拉尔斯身上就要发生神奇的事了! \N{\rENG}Something incredible is going to happen to Lars!
